Persona 1: The Enthusiastic Home Cook

Name: Aisha
Age: 34
Background: Loves cooking and experimenting with flavours
Goals:

Share favourite recipes

Learn new dishes from others
Motivations: Community, creativity
Concerns:

Getting proper credit for her recipes

Recipes being altered and misattributed

Persona 2: The Busy Participant

Name: Mark
Age: 41
Background: Full-time worker, limited time to cook
Goals:

Quick, reliable recipes

Clear instructions and ingredients
Motivations: Convenience, practicality
Concerns:

Complicated recipes

Missing allergen or dietary information

Persona 3: The Cultural Traditionalist

Name: Lina
Age: 56
Background: Cooks traditional family recipes passed down generations
Goals:

Preserve cultural authenticity

Share selectively and respectfully
Motivations: Heritage, respect
Concerns:

Cultural appropriation

Pressure to share “secret” family recipes.
